The '''Shadow Wyrm''' is a [[superior]] variant of the [[wyrm]]. It has a chance of spawning after purchasing the unlock ''Bigger and Badder'' for 150 [[Slayer reward point]]s from any [[Slayer master]]. Shadow Wyrms cannot be safespotted like regular wyrms in the slayer only area, but [[Protect from Magic]] will prevent all damage while at range.

==Drops==
''In addition to 100% drops and tertiary drops, superior slayer monsters will always roll 3 additional items, of which only 1 roll may be from the superior unique table. The other rolls are performed on the regular counterpart's table; their displayed drop chances represent a single roll.''

